{
  "stem": "19969.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 61.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Well, it was about a hundred yards from the guard tower.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I followed along.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "There was a, a-- I was just immediately outside of the cement-- of the barbed-wire fence was a path maybe 4 feet wide that led to all of the guard towers.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And outside of the path was a moat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I call it a 'moat' because it was a-- had been constructed and held water.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And the water came from the Amper River, which ran through the, the city of Dachau.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And it was-- it was filled with water.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I was on the outside of the path.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Well, I followed along the edge of that moat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And there was a line of trees all the way along that moat.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And I got down then to-- when I saw the entrance to the prison area.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And there was a building or several buildings right at the entrance.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "It was one building that bridged the entrance.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And I immediately assumed that was-- what we, in American parlance would call-- a guardhouse.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "It's where the guards slept on their-- on shift.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "The Germans call it a [GERMAN], I found out later.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Well, I was standing there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "All of a sudden-- at that time, the first thing I saw was several hundred bodies lying inside in an open space near the-- this gate to the prison area.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And there were several hundred dead people lying there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Most had been stripped nude, no clothing on them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And I, I didn't see any live people in there at that, that moment.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "But just a few moments later, the whole place erupted.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And the prisoners started streaming out of the barracks.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
